column7: buttontext
column29: If you could press a button to skip tomorrow, would you? Assume you still complete all the things you would normally complete, and remember the day normally, you just don't experience it. (mg9zk0t)
column30: How satisfied are you with life as a whole these days? (mwhc2vc)
column31: How enjoyable is your life these days? (l1z3onc)
